WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 13]

02:01.350 --> 02:02.900
Oh, where's your master?

02:04.280 --> 02:05.210
Wu Zhiqi's here again.

02:07.870 --> 02:08.740
Your master said

02:09.120 --> 02:10.540
if Wu Zhiqi can beat him,

02:11.150 --> 02:12.540
your Star Stone will be Wu's.

02:12.750 --> 02:13.500
Is that true?

02:14.710 --> 02:16.890
Maybe the fragment of the Star Stone

02:18.120 --> 02:19.170
that Wu Zhiqi has now

02:19.170 --> 02:19.850
was won from your master?

02:21.280 --> 02:21.940
Hard to say.

02:29.000 --> 02:29.690
Did it burn you?

02:32.840 --> 02:34.260
I just can't see very well.

02:35.430 --> 02:36.380
I'm not blind yet.

02:51.940 --> 02:56.780
♪A silent parting spreads like a sea of fog♪

02:57.980 --> 03:01.820
♪How do you say goodbye without regret?♪

03:02.430 --> 03:03.100
There.

03:03.870 --> 03:05.130
Your mother's eye problem

03:05.360 --> 03:06.260
isn't your fault.

03:12.560 --> 03:13.980
She was from a Flood Dragon branch.

03:15.560 --> 03:16.690
They lived underground all year,

03:18.430 --> 03:19.540
never seeing the light.

03:20.080 --> 03:21.260
Then she fell in love with my father.

03:22.190 --> 03:23.410
Ignoring her family's opposition,

03:24.030 --> 03:24.850
she married him

03:25.310 --> 03:26.690
and came to live on the surface.

03:29.150 --> 03:30.220
She always said...

03:32.800 --> 03:33.290
love...

03:35.190 --> 03:36.610
can bring a person

03:38.470 --> 03:39.410
from darkness to light.

03:41.750 --> 03:42.540
Only,

03:43.360 --> 03:44.610
her branch of the clan

03:45.870 --> 03:47.130
had lived underground so long

03:48.000 --> 03:49.980
that their eyes couldn't handle the sun's glare.

03:51.120 --> 03:51.890
Slowly,

03:54.360 --> 03:55.610
she went blind.

04:00.120 --> 04:00.820
See?

04:02.800 --> 04:03.780
Love can also bring a person

04:04.280 --> 04:05.820
from light to darkness.

04:07.680 --> 04:08.220
Isn't that right?

04:11.860 --> 04:16.180
♪Moon, oh moon, why veil your light in frost?♪

04:16.190 --> 04:17.340
My mother once said

04:17.710 --> 04:18.450
two people

04:20.120 --> 04:21.410
are like two different rivers.

04:22.390 --> 04:23.540
To merge into one,

04:24.720 --> 04:26.660
they must change their own courses.

04:28.070 --> 04:29.700
Even if the world goes dark...

04:33.000 --> 04:33.810
two people in love

04:35.600 --> 04:37.370
can always see each other.

04:39.060 --> 04:42.060
♪Don't forget, don't forget♪

04:42.260 --> 04:45.140
♪Let the moonlight gently sway♪

04:45.300 --> 04:47.940
♪Ripples dance in silver glow♪

04:47.940 --> 04:51.300
♪A harbor warm from yesterday♪

04:51.420 --> 04:54.260
♪Hair turns white in time's flow♪

04:54.500 --> 04:57.300
♪You rest upon my shoulder♪

04:57.500 --> 05:01.580
♪Take me back where we belong♪

05:04.220 --> 05:09.020
♪Moon, oh moon, paint my cheeks so red♪

05:09.420 --> 05:15.180
♪Light my path through the crowds ahead♪

05:15.820 --> 05:21.260
♪In my dreams, I hear you softly whisper♪

05:21.980 --> 05:29.700
♪This fleeting moment we can't reclaim♪

05:30.660 --> 05:32.300
♪Still feels like forever♪

05:43.950 --> 05:44.660
It's dark.

05:46.160 --> 05:47.020
Let's head home.

05:49.160 --> 05:50.140
It's already dark?

05:54.630 --> 05:55.510
No wonder

05:56.140 --> 05:57.370
I can't see clearly.

06:06.190 --> 06:07.250
Your master has

06:07.270 --> 06:09.070
extraordinary experience and skills,

06:10.010 --> 06:10.950
yet even he doesn't know

06:10.950 --> 06:12.230
where you came from.

06:14.480 --> 06:15.250
Still,

06:15.950 --> 06:17.370
the legendary demon monk

06:18.190 --> 06:19.930
actually stays behind to watch the house,

06:20.560 --> 06:21.610
teaching a child.

06:22.800 --> 06:23.660
Aren't you curious?

06:25.000 --> 06:25.730
I am.

06:28.510 --> 06:29.700
I ask him often,

06:30.680 --> 06:31.900
but he just stays quiet.

06:32.750 --> 06:34.050
Probably he has

06:34.190 --> 06:35.290
some unspoken pain.

06:36.600 --> 06:38.210
Since I was young,

06:38.510 --> 06:39.900
he rarely talked about himself.

06:41.120 --> 06:42.290
He just taught me skills day after day.

06:43.310 --> 06:44.220
I used to ask him,

06:45.390 --> 06:47.140
what's the use of learning all this?

06:47.720 --> 06:48.900
Can it catch more fish?

06:51.360 --> 06:52.460
What did your master say?

06:54.120 --> 06:54.780
He said...

06:59.040 --> 06:59.900
it's to survive.

07:07.830 --> 07:08.700
Do you think

07:09.830 --> 07:10.850
Xie Lingxi knows

07:12.310 --> 07:14.020
where the Star Stone is?

07:15.870 --> 07:16.540
Possibly.

07:20.190 --> 07:21.410
But it's been a long time

07:21.830 --> 07:23.410
since you've mentioned the Star Stone.

07:27.360 --> 07:28.410
Finding it

07:31.390 --> 07:32.490
means leaving here.

07:35.720 --> 07:36.290
You've changed.

07:39.800 --> 07:40.780
Before, you'd say

07:41.720 --> 07:42.730
finding the Star Stone

07:43.720 --> 07:45.140
would allow you to leave.

07:50.000 --> 07:51.020
After we get out,

07:54.830 --> 07:56.540
will we still live like this?

07:58.270 --> 07:59.100
Of course not.

08:05.000 --> 08:05.850
Once we're out,

08:06.920 --> 08:08.540
you'll become even more beautiful.

08:09.600 --> 08:10.900
No more white hair.

08:12.560 --> 08:13.660
And your eyes

08:14.920 --> 08:16.540
will see the stars again.

08:20.680 --> 08:22.250
Who says I can't see the stars now?

08:22.980 --> 08:29.460
♪I walk into a heartbreak burning bright♪

08:29.780 --> 08:36.260
♪Crash into a heart wall, bitter and soft♪

08:36.280 --> 08:37.270
Actually...

08:38.350 --> 08:39.530
as time goes by,

08:41.080 --> 08:42.770
I don't want to leave as much anymore.

08:46.870 --> 08:47.890
I like it here.

08:51.390 --> 08:52.650
That's why I need to find out

08:54.390 --> 08:55.490
why those killers

08:57.150 --> 08:57.940
destroyed

08:57.960 --> 08:59.420
such beautiful times.

09:10.380 --> 09:11.190
What's wrong?

09:39.200 --> 09:41.280
Thanks for the everlasting flower.

09:42.080 --> 09:43.890
I lost the bet, fair and square.

09:45.560 --> 09:47.060
I'm just curious,

09:48.360 --> 09:50.010
why did you give me this?

09:50.600 --> 09:51.980
Did Ji Ling tell you to?

09:56.320 --> 09:58.490
When you said your love for me

09:59.360 --> 10:00.970
is like this everlasting flower,

10:00.970 --> 10:01.820
that it'll never wither,

10:02.840 --> 10:03.530
was that sincere?

10:04.270 --> 10:05.060
I'm just good at acting.

10:05.870 --> 10:06.770
I've been around you.

10:08.750 --> 10:09.460
I picked it up from you.

10:12.750 --> 10:14.190
Sometimes good acting

10:14.320 --> 10:15.660
comes from true feelings.

10:19.670 --> 10:20.370
Is it pretty?

10:31.000 --> 10:31.940
Master Chi Wen,

10:32.780 --> 10:34.090
the Star Stone

10:34.270 --> 10:35.710
is already within reach.

10:37.960 --> 10:38.730
So,

10:39.910 --> 10:41.220
how about

10:41.550 --> 10:42.940
we just get married here?

10:43.510 --> 10:43.820
Hey...

10:46.360 --> 10:47.610
How can you just do it casually?

10:48.320 --> 10:50.180
I meant while we're at it!

10:51.200 --> 10:52.820
Don't twist my meaning.

10:54.510 --> 10:55.700
The real killer's still hidden.

10:56.870 --> 10:57.580
That demon

10:57.870 --> 10:59.340
could possess you at any moment.

10:59.840 --> 11:00.650
To avoid more trouble,

11:01.510 --> 11:02.060
I don't agree.

11:02.960 --> 11:03.730
Once we get the Star Stone,

11:04.120 --> 11:04.940
we leave immediately.

11:05.790 --> 11:06.650
So you're worried about me?

11:10.750 --> 11:11.610
Don't worry.

11:13.870 --> 11:15.100
I've already figured it out.

11:35.030 --> 11:35.820
I... I smell it.

11:40.320 --> 11:40.940
It's realgar.

11:42.670 --> 11:44.890
As expected of a well-read pharmacology genius.

11:45.720 --> 11:46.900
You can even smell that.

11:47.750 --> 11:48.490
I am

11:48.720 --> 11:50.100
a well-read pharmacology genius.

12:02.600 --> 12:03.420
It really works.

12:11.750 --> 12:12.130
It works...

12:27.120 --> 12:27.530
Stay there.

12:29.080 --> 12:29.420
Here.

12:31.750 --> 12:32.420
Enjoy your meal.

12:34.200 --> 12:34.700
I'll pick it up.

13:13.150 --> 13:14.410
Even getting a cup

13:15.240 --> 13:16.610
needs someone's help.

13:18.120 --> 13:19.580
So you're upset, right?

13:20.750 --> 13:22.730
For centuries,

13:22.750 --> 13:23.870
you were a demon of legend,

13:24.240 --> 13:24.850
now trapped

13:25.320 --> 13:27.850
in a body with weak magic

13:28.080 --> 13:30.180
that can't even see the world.

13:31.150 --> 13:32.200
If it were me,

13:34.000 --> 13:35.370
I'd be upset too.

13:43.030 --> 13:44.340
When we get out,

13:47.390 --> 13:49.220
I'll blindfold you,

13:50.000 --> 13:50.890
and then

13:51.480 --> 13:52.980
toss you onto the street.

13:56.670 --> 13:57.370
Okay.

13:59.390 --> 14:00.100
Deal.

14:01.910 --> 14:02.220
Here.

14:04.670 --> 14:05.730
Have your meal now.

14:07.450 --> 14:07.950
Right here.

14:13.780 --> 14:19.700
♪You are a rising tide, bringing a melody of highs and lows♪

14:20.780 --> 14:26.980
♪All my troubles are forgotten here♪

14:27.500 --> 14:33.820
♪Only you and I remain in our tiny world♪

14:34.900 --> 14:40.860
♪If you're a little boat, I'll be your mast♪

14:42.020 --> 14:47.940
♪You are a painting, beautiful even without color♪

14:49.020 --> 14:55.100
♪I miss the furrow between your brows so true♪

14:55.660 --> 15:01.820
♪So don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

15:12.270 --> 15:13.420
I made you a walking stick.

15:15.790 --> 15:16.250
Try it.

15:17.440 --> 15:18.220
See if you like it.

15:27.840 --> 15:28.340
No.

15:29.960 --> 15:30.650
Just try it.

15:33.840 --> 15:34.300
No!

16:33.080 --> 16:34.180
You old geezer.

16:34.670 --> 16:36.250
I look like a young man.

16:36.440 --> 16:37.650
You said it: look like.

16:39.440 --> 16:39.980
Just wait.

16:41.630 --> 16:42.940
I'll get stronger and come back.

16:51.120 --> 16:52.460
After all these years,

16:52.960 --> 16:53.850
Wu Zhiqi

16:54.240 --> 16:56.630
has never beaten your master even once.

17:03.160 --> 17:04.510
Though he comes

17:05.030 --> 17:07.270
to challenge you every month,

17:07.320 --> 17:08.500
Master, you don't seem

17:09.070 --> 17:10.140
to hate him.

17:11.030 --> 17:12.900
It feels more like old friends reuniting,

17:14.270 --> 17:15.460
not enemies.

17:21.640 --> 17:22.900
I am a fallen soul,

17:23.830 --> 17:25.560
wandering alone in the world.

17:26.310 --> 17:27.490
What old friends would I have?

17:29.750 --> 17:30.660
I've been bored too long.

17:31.680 --> 17:32.980
A bit of drama

17:34.310 --> 17:35.180
is a nice change.

17:36.510 --> 17:37.490
But Wu Zhiqi's obsession

17:38.400 --> 17:40.050
with the Star Stone runs deep.

17:41.070 --> 17:42.420
What if he snaps

17:42.790 --> 17:43.940
and loses himself?

17:44.830 --> 17:45.770
What are you worried about?

17:47.350 --> 17:48.250
What if he resorts to murder

17:50.440 --> 17:51.380
or outright theft?

18:17.880 --> 18:18.420
Father.

18:23.720 --> 18:24.180
Di Zhu?

18:28.480 --> 18:29.350
Father.

18:30.110 --> 18:31.220
Go back now.

18:32.070 --> 18:33.290
Get some good rest.

18:54.550 --> 18:55.800
I was worried your Word Magic

18:55.800 --> 18:56.860
might suddenly fail again.

19:00.510 --> 19:01.660
The Star Stone should be in there.

19:02.220 --> 19:02.660
Let's go.

19:09.400 --> 19:09.860
Careful.

19:16.000 --> 19:17.570
What are you waiting for? Get in here.

19:18.340 --> 19:19.080
Coming!

19:44.240 --> 19:44.660
Move.

20:08.750 --> 20:10.570
I thought you wanted to spar again.

20:12.510 --> 20:13.620
Why did you bring me here?

20:14.350 --> 20:15.250
You'll know once we're inside.

20:43.510 --> 20:44.200
Careful.

20:44.200 --> 20:46.500
[One thousand years ago, Star Stone Cave]

20:47.820 --> 20:48.450
Move.

20:50.940 --> 20:55.380
[One hundred fifty years ago, Star Stone Cave]

21:00.540 --> 21:03.500
[Fifty years ago, Star Stone Cave]

21:21.420 --> 21:23.660
[One thousand years ago]

21:23.660 --> 21:28.140
[One hundred fifty years ago]

21:28.140 --> 21:32.380
[Fifty years ago]

21:39.000 --> 21:39.780
Let me go first.

21:40.590 --> 21:41.220
In case there's danger.

22:05.240 --> 22:06.010
Who are you?

22:07.030 --> 22:07.730
Why are you here?

22:09.440 --> 22:10.090
Who are you?

22:11.790 --> 22:12.700
My name is Tian Di.
[*"Tian Di" means "heaven and earth"]

22:13.790 --> 22:14.290
Tian Di?

22:15.750 --> 22:16.940
What an arrogant name.

22:18.480 --> 22:19.420
Why are you here?

22:20.550 --> 22:21.620
I've always been here.

22:22.880 --> 22:23.570
No reason.

22:25.440 --> 22:26.860
But I've never seen strangers before.

22:37.350 --> 22:38.900
Since you've been here so long,

22:40.240 --> 22:40.980
tell me,

22:42.550 --> 22:43.530
where is the Star Stone?

22:48.970 --> 22:49.920
I...

22:52.110 --> 22:53.160
am the Star Stone.

23:08.540 --> 23:13.860
[Hurricane Catastrophe]

24:40.680 --> 24:41.420
Little spider,

24:42.950 --> 24:44.490
where are you going today?

25:00.790 --> 25:01.470
Tasty.

25:03.110 --> 25:03.860
What's this?

25:04.480 --> 25:05.330
It just rained,

25:06.030 --> 25:06.900
so some mushrooms grew.

25:07.640 --> 25:08.810
I picked them from the mountain.

25:10.750 --> 25:11.810
What's rain?

25:16.750 --> 25:17.380
Thank you.

25:18.350 --> 25:19.810
You taught me to speak,

25:20.510 --> 25:21.090
to read,

25:21.960 --> 25:23.900
to control my power

25:24.640 --> 25:25.420
and not to harm people.

25:26.400 --> 25:27.940
You even cook all this good food for me.

25:29.440 --> 25:30.980
Let me give you a spell in return.

25:33.500 --> 25:36.660
♪I raise my face, and snow veils my eyes♪

25:36.740 --> 25:39.540
♪Yet a glimmer shines through...♪

25:42.520 --> 25:43.930
This is a petrification spell.

25:45.080 --> 25:46.530
It can turn anything

25:46.870 --> 25:47.690
into stone.

25:47.740 --> 25:48.540
♪I close my eyes...♪

25:48.560 --> 25:50.250
It can protect you

25:50.950 --> 25:51.770
when you're in danger.

25:52.670 --> 25:53.580
But I hope

25:53.950 --> 25:55.180
you never have to use it,

25:56.470 --> 25:57.900
and never face danger.

25:59.150 --> 26:00.290
Why are you giving this to me?

26:01.830 --> 26:03.220
Because you're a good person.

26:03.220 --> 26:07.380
♪Ah, don't be sad for me♪

26:07.860 --> 26:16.740
♪Ah, if it hurts, grow a flower♪

26:21.960 --> 26:22.420
No.

26:24.440 --> 26:25.900
The longevity peach should be in the left hand.

26:28.920 --> 26:29.290
Chieftain,

26:31.750 --> 26:33.010
may I take a look at this clay figurine?

26:35.590 --> 26:36.420
This one's fake!

26:37.920 --> 26:39.180
All things begin in chaos

26:40.590 --> 26:41.490
and form heaven and earth.

26:42.240 --> 26:43.620
That's the origin of my name.

26:45.240 --> 26:46.420
Hundreds of years ago,

26:47.200 --> 26:48.890
I was just a stone from beyond the sky.

26:49.920 --> 26:51.650
By chance, I fell onto the land of Aodeng.

26:52.590 --> 26:54.640
Because my surface shimmered like stars,

26:55.480 --> 26:57.050
you called me the Star Stone.

26:57.880 --> 26:58.620
Later,

26:59.070 --> 27:00.140
I took human form.

27:00.830 --> 27:03.210
Through fate, I met Wu Zhiqi.

27:03.880 --> 27:04.490
After that,

27:05.550 --> 27:07.030
I've stayed here ever since.

27:10.270 --> 27:11.130
Who are you?

27:12.200 --> 27:13.280
Why are you here?

27:14.720 --> 27:16.070
We're from the Shilin Sect.

27:17.240 --> 27:18.160
We're here to save you.

27:20.770 --> 27:21.460
Save me?

27:23.310 --> 27:24.730
Wu Zhiqi has you tied up

27:24.790 --> 27:26.020
and locked away here for so long.

27:27.070 --> 27:28.290
Don't you want to be saved?

27:28.920 --> 27:30.220
He didn't imprison me.

27:31.350 --> 27:32.490
He's protecting me.

27:34.110 --> 27:35.600
Wu Zhiqi is a good man.

27:36.400 --> 27:37.180
He said

27:37.750 --> 27:39.090
I'm a weapon.

27:39.960 --> 27:42.140
Once out of control, I could bring great disasters.

27:44.880 --> 27:46.250
So I can't leave.

27:48.480 --> 27:50.050
Back then, I stole the Star Stone,

27:50.790 --> 27:52.490
thinking it could cure illness

27:53.680 --> 27:54.730
and raise the dead.

27:57.200 --> 27:57.940
But it turned out

28:00.000 --> 28:02.380
to be the most terrifying weapon in the world.

28:03.750 --> 28:05.090
So you imprisoned him.

28:08.920 --> 28:09.330
Yes.

28:12.070 --> 28:13.530
I had no choice but to deceive him

28:14.790 --> 28:16.570
and keep him locked away here.

28:17.510 --> 28:18.620
Wu Zhiqi deceived you.

28:22.010 --> 28:23.800
Am I not a weapon?

28:24.550 --> 28:25.860
You truly are the most terrifying

28:26.000 --> 28:27.180
weapon in the world.

28:28.270 --> 28:29.820
But he imprisoned you here

28:30.200 --> 28:31.800
not to protect you

28:32.110 --> 28:33.090
or protect the world.

28:33.920 --> 28:35.250
He just wanted to use you.

28:36.480 --> 28:37.180
Use me?

28:38.920 --> 28:40.050
By midnight tonight,

28:41.400 --> 28:43.100
he'll send you to the battlefield,

28:45.790 --> 28:48.420
making you a divine weapon to slaughter humans.

28:50.750 --> 28:51.420
I don't believe it.

28:54.030 --> 28:54.980
He's a good man.

28:57.750 --> 28:58.700
He wouldn't lie to me.

29:01.590 --> 29:02.700
Fifty years ago,

29:05.160 --> 29:06.220
the Star Stone exploded,

29:06.750 --> 29:07.810
laying waste for miles.

29:08.510 --> 29:09.860
Not a single human survived.

29:10.830 --> 29:13.290
The Green Apes managed to survive

29:14.640 --> 29:16.050
with demon magic,

29:17.160 --> 29:19.380
but they fell to an incurable disease

29:19.880 --> 29:20.770
due to the explosion's intense light.

29:21.400 --> 29:23.520
My clan grew weaker,

29:23.830 --> 29:25.580
like wilted plants,

29:26.160 --> 29:27.610
losing all vitality,

29:28.160 --> 29:29.180
suffering unbearably.

29:30.240 --> 29:31.380
I couldn't cure them,

29:33.000 --> 29:35.570
but I couldn't bear to see them in such pain.

29:38.720 --> 29:39.700
So I used

29:39.720 --> 29:41.460
the petrification spell.

29:44.270 --> 29:45.810
But later I found out

29:46.640 --> 29:47.840
I was wrong.

29:48.830 --> 29:51.050
I didn't stop their suffering.

29:52.030 --> 29:53.460
Instead, I brought them

29:53.510 --> 29:55.090
endless torment.

30:17.680 --> 30:18.460
Who are you?

30:22.240 --> 30:23.390
You've been deceived.

30:23.980 --> 30:25.960
Though their bodies have turned to stone,

30:26.140 --> 30:28.430
their spirits remain conscious.

30:29.310 --> 30:31.490
They were supposed to die quickly

30:31.550 --> 30:32.660
from the pain of their illness,

30:32.720 --> 30:33.900
freed from their misery.

30:34.880 --> 30:35.380
But you

30:36.070 --> 30:38.050
trapped them here,

30:38.310 --> 30:39.670
suffering for all eternity,

30:40.160 --> 30:41.810
with no end.

30:43.000 --> 30:44.030
That's impossible...

30:46.750 --> 30:47.620
That's impossible!

30:50.240 --> 30:51.460
We were born with one more eye

30:51.480 --> 30:52.730
than others.

30:53.200 --> 30:54.480
That's why we're called

30:55.030 --> 30:56.400
Six-Eyed Butterflies.

30:57.830 --> 30:58.620
And,

30:59.160 --> 31:00.330
we can hear sounds

31:00.350 --> 31:01.980
that others can't.

31:02.050 --> 31:03.820
Do you want to hear them?

31:24.680 --> 31:26.490
It hurts so much!

31:29.830 --> 31:30.950
Wu Zhiqi,

31:31.160 --> 31:33.140
save me please!

31:33.400 --> 31:35.460
Just let me die!

31:59.640 --> 32:00.490
For fifty years,

32:03.720 --> 32:04.460
my people

32:06.200 --> 32:07.570
have been stuck here,

32:08.160 --> 32:09.510
suffering endlessly,

32:11.680 --> 32:12.970
without a glimmer of hope.

32:15.640 --> 32:17.550
Moss covers their bodies.

32:19.030 --> 32:20.980
Tian Di gave me the petrification spell,

32:22.960 --> 32:25.420
but never told me how to undo it.

32:33.830 --> 32:34.660
Why didn't you...

32:38.680 --> 32:39.290
ask him?

32:41.790 --> 32:42.860
Because Tian Di...

32:47.640 --> 32:49.810
also died in that explosion.

32:55.590 --> 32:56.900
I used the Heavenly Punishment Lock

32:57.720 --> 32:59.330
to imprison myself in the Blackwater River,

33:00.550 --> 33:01.880
praying the river

33:02.030 --> 33:03.870
would wash away my sins

33:05.070 --> 33:06.680
until the end of my life.

33:17.440 --> 33:18.460
Wu Zhiqi.

33:21.440 --> 33:22.570
Wu Zhiqi.

33:30.270 --> 33:31.050
But then,

33:32.240 --> 33:33.770
Master Chi Wen found me.

33:35.110 --> 33:37.010
The Star Stone still exists.

33:37.310 --> 33:38.620
You still have hope.

33:39.350 --> 33:40.610
Find it,

33:40.920 --> 33:42.090
undo the petrification,

33:42.550 --> 33:44.590
and make up for your mistakes.

33:50.510 --> 33:52.050
When we were drinking earlier,

33:53.160 --> 33:54.140
for a moment,

33:55.590 --> 33:56.730
I really felt we were friends

33:56.790 --> 33:58.490
who held nothing back.

34:03.680 --> 34:05.010
But for my people,

34:06.720 --> 34:07.420
forgive me.

34:11.240 --> 34:12.860
Don't touch the Star Stone.

34:13.480 --> 34:14.710
It's mine.

34:18.710 --> 34:19.460
I knew it.

34:40.000 --> 34:41.380
You dared to lie to me!

34:55.400 --> 34:57.210
You all conspired against me?

35:12.440 --> 35:13.820
Is what they said true?

35:16.030 --> 35:17.310
I once told you

35:18.230 --> 35:19.970
the world is colorful

35:20.000 --> 35:21.130
and magnificent.

35:22.880 --> 35:24.010
But in this world,

35:25.030 --> 35:26.420
there are many choices

35:27.800 --> 35:29.130
that can only be black or white.

35:31.400 --> 35:32.210
I had no choice.

35:33.800 --> 35:35.320
You also told me

35:36.550 --> 35:38.140
exchange sincerity for sincerity,

35:38.670 --> 35:39.620
that's friendship.

35:40.710 --> 35:41.820
Exchange sincerity

35:43.000 --> 35:44.250
for sincerity,

35:45.590 --> 35:46.580
that's friendship.

35:47.360 --> 35:48.620
Exchange blades for blades,

35:49.840 --> 35:50.610
that can also be friendship.

35:51.440 --> 35:52.170
Exchange blades

35:53.480 --> 35:54.260
for blades,

35:55.630 --> 35:56.490
that can also be friendship.

36:01.230 --> 36:02.380
Then which one are we?

36:04.230 --> 36:05.010
You and I...

36:08.510 --> 36:09.420
are the latter.

36:12.510 --> 36:12.940
You...

36:19.440 --> 36:20.490
So your master...

36:21.280 --> 36:22.210
Is the Star Stone.

36:43.070 --> 36:43.780
Wu Zhiqi,

36:44.480 --> 36:46.300
do you think he's still Man Man?

36:49.580 --> 36:51.020
He was possessed long ago.

36:52.030 --> 36:53.640
His target is the Star Stone too.

36:54.320 --> 36:55.650
You've been used.

36:56.480 --> 36:57.780
Why are you so quiet today?

36:58.510 --> 37:00.490
Acting all solemn and mature.

37:01.920 --> 37:02.340
Man Man,

37:03.840 --> 37:04.570
what's the name

37:05.630 --> 37:06.460
of my younger brother?

37:10.070 --> 37:10.780
See?

37:13.510 --> 37:13.940
Yuan.

37:15.280 --> 37:18.010
Your younger brother's name is Yuan.

37:19.030 --> 37:21.180
The war between humans and demons

37:21.760 --> 37:23.010
began with the Yuan Clay Incident.

37:24.190 --> 37:27.740
And "Yuan" comes from the name

37:27.800 --> 37:29.380
of Wu Zhiqi's younger brother,

37:30.550 --> 37:32.130
Yuan.

37:37.000 --> 37:38.380
Trying to sow discord between us?

37:39.880 --> 37:40.340
Man Man,

37:41.240 --> 37:42.170
combine our power,

37:42.850 --> 37:43.970
the Gale-Swept Sand.

37:48.230 --> 37:49.940
You don't even know that move?

37:50.590 --> 37:51.820
You really aren't Man Man.

39:05.190 --> 39:05.740
Lu Wuyi...

39:08.070 --> 39:09.820
Who knows what happens

39:10.370 --> 39:11.690
if we die in the illusion...

39:16.260 --> 39:17.620
Will the me out there...

39:19.000 --> 39:20.260
die too?

39:21.580 --> 39:27.580
♪If you're a kite, drifting in the world...♪

39:33.230 --> 39:34.550
Even the everlasting flower...

39:38.230 --> 39:39.340
can't last forever either.

39:42.460 --> 39:45.300
♪The wind drifts by, leaves a lonely light♪

39:45.500 --> 39:49.940
♪You and I stay, without a word tonight...♪

39:54.800 --> 39:56.200
Everyone says

39:58.590 --> 40:01.340
the Dragon Deity feels no joy or sorrow,

40:03.030 --> 40:04.340
his heart like a sacred altar,

40:06.230 --> 40:07.260
untouched by dust...

40:11.480 --> 40:12.530
I've never seen...

40:14.230 --> 40:15.690
that look on your face before.

40:22.510 --> 40:23.820
You do care about me,

40:26.550 --> 40:27.400
don't you?

40:30.920 --> 40:32.340
I have one more thing to say...

40:33.980 --> 40:39.820
♪You gently guard every moment I'm lost...♪

40:39.840 --> 40:40.380
Go ahead.

40:40.980 --> 40:46.700
♪The world is vast, where will you settle?♪

40:46.710 --> 40:47.630
Lu Wuyi?

40:50.150 --> 40:51.050
Lu Wuyi?

40:56.070 --> 40:57.040
My love for Di Zhu

40:57.760 --> 40:59.930
is like this beautiful everlasting flower!

41:00.760 --> 41:01.570
It will never fade.

41:02.260 --> 41:08.300
♪I miss the furrow between your brows so true♪

41:08.900 --> 41:14.540
♪So don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view...♪

41:21.800 --> 41:23.980
I want an honest answer from you...

41:26.960 --> 41:27.860
Are you...

41:30.320 --> 41:31.210
or are you not...

41:32.670 --> 41:33.490
Ji Ling?

41:44.620 --> 41:50.620
♪If you're the moon, I'll be falling snow♪

41:51.580 --> 41:56.940
♪Let them chase the skies, I'll stay with you below...♪

41:56.960 --> 41:57.460
Lu Wuyi...

41:58.660 --> 42:04.860
♪I truly miss the taste of your tears♪

42:04.900 --> 42:05.500
♪So please♪

42:05.660 --> 42:11.500
♪So don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

42:11.820 --> 42:12.380
♪So please♪

42:12.740 --> 42:23.380
♪So don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

42:51.620 --> 42:52.780
♪It's your light♪

42:52.980 --> 42:54.860
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

42:55.020 --> 42:58.140
♪That set the night alight♪

42:58.500 --> 43:05.020
♪And lead me through the fight♪

43:06.780 --> 43:08.660
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

43:09.100 --> 43:13.540
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

43:14.340 --> 43:16.020
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

43:16.180 --> 43:21.580
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

43:22.340 --> 43:27.740
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

43:30.060 --> 43:36.100
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

43:37.060 --> 43:39.220
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

43:39.500 --> 43:44.340
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

43:44.700 --> 43:47.020
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

43:47.220 --> 43:52.300
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

43:52.540 --> 43:54.540
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

43:54.820 --> 43:59.180
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

44:00.180 --> 44:07.140
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

44:23.700 --> 44:26.660
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

44:27.740 --> 44:31.140
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

44:31.940 --> 44:34.460
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

44:34.700 --> 44:37.780
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

44:38.180 --> 44:40.500
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

44:41.020 --> 44:45.420
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

44:45.660 --> 44:47.820
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

44:48.220 --> 44:53.180
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

44:53.420 --> 44:54.580
♪It's your light♪

44:54.780 --> 44:56.620
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

44:56.820 --> 44:59.940
♪That set the night alight♪

45:00.700 --> 45:10.140
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
